    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, i know it's serious. but like, my doctor's appointments are always such a hassle and i've been doing really well with my diet and exercise lately. i feel like my body is handling things much better than before. wouldn't a lower dose like 2mg still be enough to keep me safe since i'm so healthy now? just trying to understand if a smaller amount is actually reasonable.",
